# ------------ Weather_daemon.py ------------
# Language : python v3
# Depend : yaml-python, python-requests
# Description : Daemon that can download weather forecast on wunderground
# Long description : It's a python's script who download json's file on wunderground (You must register on wunderground). After, informations are wrote to /tmp/weather
#                    (see /etc/weather_daemon_example.conf). After you can display it on screen with conky or something else (dzen2, ...)
#
